  "english": [
    "<b>And we also learned a case like this</b> in a <i>baraita</i> (<i>Tosefta</i>, <i>Orla</i> 1:4), <b>with regard to</b> the prohibition against eating <b>the fruit of a tree during the first three years after its planting [<i>orla</i>]:</b> In the case of <b>a tree that sprouts from the trunk and from the roots</b> of an old tree, its owner is <b>obligated in <i>orla</i>,</b> since it is considered like a new tree, and the <i>orla</i> years must be counted anew. This is <b>the statement of Rabbi Meir. Rabbi Yehuda says:</b> If it sprouts <b>from the trunk,</b> the owner is <b>exempt,</b> since it is considered like a branch of the old tree, but if it grows <b>from the roots,</b> the owner is <b>obligated.</b>",
    "The Gemara comments: <b>And</b> both cases <b>are necessary</b> to be stated although they are both based on the same principle. <b>As had</b> it <b>taught us</b> only the <b>first</b> <i>halakha</i>, that of ownership, one could say that it is only <b>with regard to this</b> case that <b>Rabbi Yehuda said</b> his ruling, <b>due to</b> the fact <b>that</b> it pertains to <b>monetary matters, but with regard to <i>orla</i>, which is</b> a matter of <b>a prohibition,</b> one could <b>say</b> that <b>he concedes to Rabbi Meir. And if it was stated</b> only <b>with regard to this</b> case of <i>orla</i>, one could say that it is only <b>with regard to this</b> case that <b>Rabbi Meir said</b> his stringent ruling, <b>but with regard to that</b> case, one could <b>say</b> that <b>he concedes to Rabbi Yehuda.</b> It is therefore <b>necessary</b> to state both disputes.",
    "§ The mishna teaches: <b>Rabbi Shimon said: Any</b> vegetables <b>that the</b> owner of the <b>upper</b> garden <b>can stretch out</b> his hand and take, those vegetables are his, and the rest belong to the owner of the lower garden. In <b>the school of Rabbi Yannai they say: And</b> this is only so <b>provided that he does not force</b> himself, but simply stretches out his hand in the usual manner.",
    "<b>Rav Anan, and some say</b> it was <b>Rabbi Yirmeya, raised a dilemma:</b> If the owner of the upper garden can <b>reach its leaves, but</b> he <b>cannot reach its roots,</b> or if he can <b>reach its roots but</b> he <b>cannot reach its leaves, what</b> is the <i>halakha</i>? Is the plant considered to be within his reach or not? No answer was found for this question, and the Gemara concludes: The dilemma <b>shall stand</b> unresolved.",
    "<b>Efrayim the scribe, a student of Reish Lakish, says in the name of Reish Lakish:</b> The <b><i>halakha</i></b> is <b>in accordance with</b> the opinion of <b>Rabbi Shimon. They stated</b> this case <b>before</b> the Persian <b>King Shapur,</b> who expressed an interest in this legal issue, and <b>he said to them: Let us offer praise [<i>apiryon</i>] to Rabbi Shimon.</b> He too felt that this was the best resolution."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וּתְנַן נָמֵי גַּבֵּי עָרְלָה כִּי הַאי גַוְונָא: אִילָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַיּוֹצֵא מִן הַגֶּזַע וּמִן הַשָּׁרָשִׁין – חַיָּיב בְּעָרְלָה,",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דִּבְרֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Meir, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2068\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Meir\" data-name-he=\"רבי מאיר\">רַבִּי מֵאִיר</span>. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span> אוֹמֵר: מִן הַגֶּזַע –",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "פָּטוּר, מִן הַשָּׁרָשִׁין – חַיָּיב. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וּצְרִיכִי, דְּאִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אַשְׁמוֹעִינַן קַמַּיְיתָא: בְּהָא קָאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשּׁוּם דְּמָמוֹנָא, אֲבָל גַּבֵּי עָרְלָה דְּאִיסּוּרָא –",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵימָא מוֹדֵי לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Meir, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2068\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Meir\" data-name-he=\"רבי מאיר\">לְרַבִּי מֵאִיר</span>. וְאִי אִיתְּמַר בְּהָא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּהָא קָאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Meir, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2068\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Meir\" data-name-he=\"רבי מאיר\">רַבִּי מֵאִיר</span>, אֲבָל בְּהַהִיא – אֵימָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹדֵי לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">לְרַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span>, צְרִיכִי.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"532\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"309\" data-sentence-id=\"2\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-15428\">רַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-15428\">שִׁמְעוֹן</span>: כֹּל שֶׁהָעֶלְיוֹן יָכוֹל לִפְשׁוֹט [וְכוּ׳].<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"533\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמְרִי דְּבֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yannai, son II, first-generation II Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1814\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yannai, son II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ינאי רבה\">רַבִּי יַנַּאי</span>: וּבִלְבַד שֶׁלֹּא יֵאָנֵס.",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בָּעֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Anan, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2453\" data-full-name=\"Rav Anan\" data-name-he=\"רב ענן\">רַב עָנָן</span>, וְאִיתֵּימָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II, third and fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1952\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ירמיה\">רַבִּי יִרְמְיָה</span>: מַגִּיעַ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְנוֹפוֹ וְאֵין מַגִּיעַ לְעִיקָּרוֹ, מַגִּיעַ לְעִיקָּרוֹ וְאֵין",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַגִּיעַ לְנוֹפוֹ, מַאי? תֵּיקוּ.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"534\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר אֶפְרַיִם סָפְרָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תַּלְמִידוֹ שֶׁל <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2879\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן לקיש\">רֵישׁ לָקִישׁ</span> מִשּׁוּם רֵישׁ לָקִישׁ:",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">כְּרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>. אַמְרוּהָ קַמֵּיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Gemara relates, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2705\" data-full-name=\"Gemara relates\" data-name-he=\"שבור מלכא\">דְּשַׁבּוּר מַלְכָּא</span>,",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲמַר לְהוּ: אָפְרִין נִמְטְיֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">לְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"535\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "930px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><strong><big>הֲדַרַן עֲלָךְ הַבַּיִת וְהָעֲלִיָּיה וּסְלִיקָא לַהּ מַסֶּכֶת בָּבָא מְצִיעָא</big></strong>",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אִילָן הַיּוֹצֵא מִן הַגֶּזַע <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וכו&#x27;</span>.</b> בלוקח אילן אחד בתוך של חבירו דקי\"ל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בבבא בתרא (<a href=\"/bava_batra/81a\">דף פא.</a>) דדברי הכל לא קנה קרקע ואילן קטן היוצא (מן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הגזע או) מן השרשין לית דינא ולית דיינא דקרקע גמורה היא ומן הגזע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי רבי מאיר סבר שדי נופו בתר עיקרו והתם מפרש מאי גזע ומאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שרשין גזע כל שרואה פני חמה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שרשין שאין רואין פני חמה ואע\"ג",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דשבח נוף העליון לבעל האילן כדקתני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התם הגדילו לא ישפה התם הוא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאדעתא דהכי נחת שכל זמן שיהא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ראויין לעשות פרי יהא בקרקע וישא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ענף ופירי אבל אילן אחר העולה מן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הגזע אילנא אחרינא הוא: <b>חַיָּיב בְּעָרְלָה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גרסי' לר\"מ דאילן הוא לעצמו דגזע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הסמוך לקרקע בתוך שלשה כקרקע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוא ואף על גב דלא מארעא ממש יניק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שדי נופו בתר עיקרו: <b>מַגִּיעַ לְעִיקָּרוֹ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ואינו</span> מַגִּיעַ לְנוֹפוֹ</b> כגון שנוטה נופו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למטה: <b>קַמֵּיהּ דְּשַׁבּוּר מַלְכָּא.</b> לי נראה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבור מלכא ממש ומלך פרס היה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ובקי בדינים ואמרוה להא דר\"ש דמתני'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קמיה וקלסה ואמר אפריון נמטייה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לר\"ש יקבל חן מאתנו על דבר זה ואית",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמרי שבור מלכא שמואל דבכמה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דוכתי קרי ליה הכי ואין מיושב בה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמאי אמרוה אי להא דר\"ש דמתני'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אטו שמואל לא הוה ידע לה למתני'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואי להא דאפרים ספרא אטו אי לא אמר ריש לקיש הלכה כר\"ש שמואל מי לא קים בדיני למיקלסיה לר\"ש עד דשמע משמיה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דריש לקיש דהלכתא כוותיה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אפריון</span>.</b> חן שלנו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 119a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    }
  ],
